https://kubernetes.gitHub.io/ingress-nginx/deploy

Use the yaml manifest don't kubectl apply yet

Copy and paste the 'raw.gitHub' link, copy yaml manifest and edit to your taste in your IDE 
 

*This ingress-controller is one I've not had issues with compared to others.

Apply: 

Kubectl apply -f <ingress.yml>

You can choose to create a network policy for your cluster refer to network policy yaml file in the repo

